	Given the JsonElement backed JsonInteger <jsonValue>
	When I compare it to the integer <value>
	Then the result should be <result>

	Examples:
		| jsonValue | value | result |
		| 1         | 1     | true   |
		| 1         | 3     | false  |
		| null      | null  | true   |
